data.description: Discover the possibilities at 6171 Old Dayton Pike in North Redbank! Sitting on over 4 acres, this spacious 2-story home offers 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, promising a world of potential. Conveniently situated, this property boasts a bedroom and a full bathroom on the main level, offering flexibility and convenience. With a total of 4 fireplaces, including one in the expansive family room/den downstairs, you'll have plenty of cozy spots to relax and unwind. The formal dining room provides an elegant space for hosting gatherings and special occasions. Upstairs, the primary bedroom offers a cozy fireplace, a walk-in closet, and a double vanity in the en suite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms and another full bathroom await you on the second level, making it perfect for a growing family or accommodating guests.Step outside to the back patio, where you can soak up the outdoors and enjoy the ample 4.24 acres of land that surround this property. Whether you have dreams of gardening, outdoor entertainment, or simply enjoying the tranquility of nature, this spacious lot offers endless possibilities. Located within 7 minutes to all that Hixson has to offer and 14 minutes to North Chattanooga, this home provides the convenience of shopping and dining while also maintaining a peaceful and private atmosphere. This property is a canvas waiting for your personal touch. With its massive potential, it's the perfect opportunity for a new owner to undertake a project and transform it into their own dream home. Schedule a viewing today and explore the potential that 6171 Old Dayton Pike has to offer! Local lenders are preferred.
